---
title: Swedish Meatballs over Egg Noodles & Baby Portobellos
description: Sorry Italians, but the Swedes may have won the meatball battle. These traditional Swedish meatballs are spiced with warm allspice and nutmeg, then tossed with rich egg noodles and mushroom cream sauce. Baking the meatballs in the oven lightens up this comfort food classic!
